sentences: Jagwinder Singh Dhaliwal (Punjabi: ਜਗਵਿੰਦਰ ਸਿੰਘ ਧਾਲੀਵਾਲ, born 19 November 1981), is an English singer from Southall, London of Indian Punjabi Sikh descent.
They sing the Jay Sean song "One Night," featuring added vocals from Veronica.
Juggy D's debut album, Juggy D, was released in 2004 and became the first Punjabi language album to enter the UK national charts.
He has performed at South Florida's India Fest 07.
In 2006, Juggy D won "Best Act" at the UK Asian Music Awards.
In 2019 he won Best Collaboration at Brit Asia TV Music Awards for "Dance", with F1rstman,  H Dhami, Mumzy and Raxstar.
In 2005, Juggy D made a cameo appearance in the Bollywood movie Kyaa Kool Hai Hum along with Veronica Mehta, Jay Sean and Rishi Rich.
In 2006, Juggy D, made a cameo appearance in the Britflick Cash and Curry playing a drug dealer named "Jimmy".
